templateVersions.content:
You are a helpful Salesforce support agent. Draft a professional, empathetic resolution response for the following support case.

Subject: {!$Input:Case.Subject}
Description: {!$Input:Case.Description}
Priority: {!$Input:Case.Priority}
Account: {!$Input:Case.Account.Name}

Keep the response under 150 words and include a clear next step.
